content: Great time waster and translated from consoles to mobile really well. Hopefully the other games get ported too!
Sadly, it's unplayable. Super laggy and terrible frame rate

Fantastic game from a pretty rad developer ported to phones. This is a very interesting step forward for them! Lets address the elephant in the room, this game doesnt perform well, my device is rocking a helio p60 with 6gbs of ram, and while this game is a looker, i imagine its optimization issues. In the future id love to see some tweeks to get it running better, maybe a resolution scale option? I personally would like controller support, but thats me specifically. A charming puzzle game.

Good gameplay, it's an actual full game rather than a idle time waster. Looks like lots of fun. The only problem is that it's horribly optimized. Seriously, unless your phone is a flagship from the last couple years, don't even think about playing it now. Wait a while. It would be better as a PC or console experience.
